Package: slackapi
Title: `Slack Web API` Client
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jon", "Harmon", , "jonthegeek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4781-4346"))
Description: A client to interact with the `Slack Web API` 
    <https://api.slack.com/web>. The `Slack Web API` is an interface for 
    querying information from and enacting change in a `Slack` workspace.
